Yeo Wool.

181
00:21:43,196 --> 00:21:45,324
Pomôž mi.

182
00:21:46,222 --> 00:21:50,046
Pomôž mi, prosím.

183
00:21:52,878 --> 00:21:55,394
Prosím...

184
00:22:06,092 --> 00:22:10,283
